# Goal
int32 mover_id
float64 x          # mm
float64 y          # mm
float64 velocity   # mm/s, 0 = use default
---
# Result
bool success
uint32 error_id    # 0 if success, otherwise TwinCAT error code
string message
float64 final_x
float64 final_y
---
# Feedback
float64 current_x
float64 current_y
float64 distance_remaining